room_title: Escape room "Pirates Parlor" by The Cube Escape Rooms in Santa Barbara
room_description: You’ve been taken captive and your future is at least uncertain! However, an opportunity arose, as the pirates celebrating their successful attack overdone a bit. Here’s your chance to exploit their temporary weakness and get out their ship. You will have to use many of your skills as the pirates secured the ship before starting their party. You have an hour to outwit them and free yourselves from their ship!
